Helpers for creating output files

outHelpers.Rd

Helpers for creating output files

makeTable(dvn, fit, model, tabletype)

makeFigure(fit, type)

Arguments

dvn

input object from dyadVarNames()
type

input character to indicate whether parameters "free" or "equated" in estimation
param

input character for what kind of parameter is being scripted ("act", "apim_part", "mim_part", "cf")
lvar

input character for whether scripting helpers target latent "X" or :Y" indicator variables in dvn
lvxname

input character to (arbitrarily) name LV X in lavaan syntax
lvyname

input character to (arbitrarily) name LV Y in lavaan syntax
partner

input character to indicate parameters for first or second dyad member

See also

Other helpers: esHelpers, outParamHelpers, scrapeHelpers, scriptHelpers, semHelpers
